                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12704787" author="junrao" created="Thu, 30 Apr 2009 20:44:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attach a fix that deals with non-existing keys in SSTables explicitly.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12704796" author="jbellis" created="Thu, 30 Apr 2009 20:57:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;If I understand what you are doing, shouldn&apos;t you take out the IOException catches that deal with the current way of doing things? e.g. in SSTable,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;            catch( IOException ex )&lt;/p&gt;
            {
                logger_.info(&quot;Bloom filter false positive&quot;, ex);
            }

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;d also like to see a test case that exercises this code path.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12704801" author="jbellis" created="Thu, 30 Apr 2009 21:07:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;sorry, I was looking at the wrong git repo.  I don&apos;t see any exceptions anymore that you&apos;d want to change, either.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12704810" author="junrao" created="Thu, 30 Apr 2009 21:59:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Add a testcase that covers the code path when a BF gives a false positive.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12704833" author="jbellis" created="Thu, 30 Apr 2009 23:00:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;thanks, looks good.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;i&apos;m not comfortable w/ introducing more code duplication, though.  what do you think of this version?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12704854" author="junrao" created="Thu, 30 Apr 2009 23:58:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;patch v2 looks good to me.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12704872" author="jbellis" created="Fri, 1 May 2009 02:25:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;committed&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12704979" author="hudson" created="Fri, 1 May 2009 13:09:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Integrated in Cassandra #55 (See &lt;a href=&quot;http://hudson.zones.apache.org/hudson/job/Cassandra/55/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://hudson.zones.apache.org/hudson/job/Cassandra/55/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br/&gt;
    avoid raising an exception in SequenceFile.next when a key does not exist (e.g. when bloom filter gives a false positive).  patch by Jun Rao; reviewed by jbellis for &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
